  "detailed_description": "Protect Mars from waves of enemies in \"Mission: Mars.\" As Sergeant Eric, lead your team through 60 intense days of battle. Choose suits, upgrade weapons to ensure the survival of humanity's future on the Red Planet.<br>GamePlay:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/c7fc720a0156b95f5cceb7b1c11e53ea.poster.avif?t=1762450799\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/c7fc720a0156b95f5cceb7b1c11e53ea.webm?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/c7fc720a0156b95f5cceb7b1c11e53ea.mp4?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dive into the arsenal of 'Mission: Mars' with a plethora of customizable suits offering diverse protection levels, a selection of 8 powerful weapons for ultimate firepower, and a team of skilled allies ready to aid your mission. Equip, upgrade, and conquer the Red Planet!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/3347ef94330c2736dd0babdd8608d608.poster.avif?t=1762450799\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/3347ef94330c2736dd0babdd8608d608.webm?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/3347ef94330c2736dd0babdd8608d608.mp4?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strategize your defense with tactical placement of mines and explosive barrels across the Martian terrain. Wipe out waves of enemies efficiently and dominate the battlefield in 'Mission: Mars'!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/26b1bbad7063e35b87391ab8e372351a.poster.avif?t=1762450799\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/26b1bbad7063e35b87391ab8e372351a.webm?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2942610/extras/26b1bbad7063e35b87391ab8e372351a.mp4?t=1762450799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><br></li><li>Realistic Graphics <br></li><li>60-Day Campaign<br></li><li>Customizable Experience (Weapons, suits, team) </li></ul>",
